{% comment %}
  Renders the display title for a cart line item.
  For CustomScale items, shows the "Product" line item property (the selected product name)
  instead of the carrier product title ("CustomScale Dynamic Product").

  Usage in your theme's cart section (e.g. main-cart-items or cart-drawer):
    {% render 'customscale-line-item-title', line_item: line_item %}

  Or with variable name 'item':
    {% render 'customscale-line-item-title', line_item: item %}
{% endcomment %}
{% if line_item.properties.Product != blank %}
  {{ line_item.properties.Product }}
{% else %}
  {{ line_item.product.title }}
{% endif %}
